import React, { useEffect, useState } from 'react'; import './Hero.css'; const Hero = () => { const [counted, setCounted] = useState(false); const [isVisible, setIsVisible] = useState(false); useEffect(() => { // Trigger animations when component mounts setCounted(true); setIsVisible(true); // Add scroll event listener for parallax effect const handleScroll = () => { const scrolled = window.pageYOffset; const parallaxElements = document.querySelectorAll('.parallax-element'); parallaxElements.forEach(element => { const speed = parseFloat(element.getAttribute('data-speed')) || 0.5; element.style.transform = `translateY(${scrolled * speed}px)`; }); }; window.addEventListener('scroll', handleScroll); return () => window.removeEventListener('scroll', handleScroll); }, []); return (
